name: Nascar
description:
This is a duffle bag made by Nascar. 
 The bag is red, black, and white and features a shoulder strap, two handles, a pocket on each side with a zip-up closure, and a zip-up closure for the main bag.
 It measures approximately 9.75 tall, 19.25 wide from left to right, and 9 deep from front to back. 
 This item comes in good pre-owned condition with some faint stains.
